{"tid":2155102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沈旭暉發表愛國愛港宣言","createTime":"2020-08-13T13:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T15:09:12.000Z","uid":104804,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"36532085e8b3623e12cdd5a76c4ce1f68cc7d7d8","tid":2155102,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:56:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/photos/a.224514904249334/3516496765051115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon%2Fphotos%2Fa.224514904249334%2F3516496765051115&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=6bdcdd9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/photos/a.224514904249334/3516496765051115</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A3LRkeA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA3LRkeA.jpg&h=fcc44435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我们是一群爱国爱港市民，对港区国安法出台后成为社会的定海神针，感到心旷神怡，怎料香港二次回归后，居然有万恶英殖余孽乱港份子渗透在我国政府，公然污蔑中华人民共和国十四亿人民尊严，感到民族感情严重受损。中国香港制造的产品，印上「中国制造」这个令十四亿同胞骄傲光荣的优质品牌，天经地义，怎料乱港份子公然主张「香港制造」非「中国制造」，更以「指白为黑」诋毁国家为「黑暴」，矛头直指「一国两制」、直指中央，行径令人发指。我们再三敦促乱港份子不要打错算盘、误判形势，不要低估中央政府和全国人民依法捍卫国家主权、维护国家利益和统一的意志和决心，对一小撮别有用心乱港分子的错误主张，我们予以最强烈谴责和坚决反对。"},{"pid":"e6d11dbfb781361b46b4f7f17b65272b2814906d","tid":2155102,"uid":104804,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T14:13:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%82%B1%E9%A8%B0%E8%8F%AF%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7%E8%A7%B8%E7%8A%AF%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E6%B6%89%E5%AB%8C%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E6%88%96%E6%95%99%E5%94%86%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2582%25B1%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25A7%25B8%25E7%258A%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%25AB%258C%25E7%2585%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%2594%2586%25E5%2588%2586%25E